comment: [Incidental or immaterial] Griffin (LAC) is in the lane without actively guarding for more than three seconds.
Jackson (DET) does not impede Griffin's (LAC) movement to the basket.

Jordan (LAC) pushes Drummond (DET) as he attempts the screen.
Jordan (LAC) and Drummond (DET) make incidental contact on their attempt to secure the rebound.
